data.description: Country living at it's best! If you have a horse, this is the property for you! Located in CISD, this 3/2 home sits on a total of 9.24 acres with a water well just minutes from Gary Schools. Nice Kitchen/dining area and spacious living room with wood burning fireplace. Large utility room with Bonus/Game Room just off carport. Nice Master Bathroom shower/tub combo. Older chicken house just across the County Road from home with another water well that sits on +/- 8.24 acres and the home sits on +/- 1 acre. Survey on file. Give me a call for a showing.
